n operator\">-</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"12\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">#3 复制</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"13\"></td><td><pre>yy\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">#复制当前光标所在的行\t\t\t</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"14\"></td><td><pre>5yy\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">#复制当前光标以及光标向下 4 行</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"15\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"16\"></td><td><pre>p<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>小写<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> \t   <span class=\"token comment\">#粘贴至当前光标下一行</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"17\"></td><td><pre>P<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>大写<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> \t   <span class=\"token comment\">#粘贴至当前光标上一行</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"18\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token o