ass=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"29\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">#5. 替换</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"30\"></td><td><pre>r\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">#๊替换当前光标标记的单个字符</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"31\"></td><td><pre>R\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">#进入 Replace 模式，连续替换，ESC 结束</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id=\"编辑模式主要用于编辑文件\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#编辑模式主要用于编辑文件\">#</a> 编辑模式：主要用于编辑文件</h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>i\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">#进入编辑模式，光标不做任何操作</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>a\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">#进入编辑模式，将当前光标往后一位</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>o       <span class=\"token comment\">#进入编辑模式，并且当前光标下添加一行空白内容</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>I       <span class=\"token comment\">#进入编辑模式，并且光标会跳转至本行的头部</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre>A\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">#进入编辑模式，将光标移动至本行的末尾</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre>O\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">#进入编辑模式，并在当前光标上添加一行空白内容</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id=\"末行模式主要用于搜索保存退出文件\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#末行模式主要用于搜索保存退出文件\">#</a> 末行模式：主要用于搜索，保存，退出文件</h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">#1. 文件保存于退出</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>w\t\t <span class=\"token comment\">#保存当前状态</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>w！\t    <span class=\"token comment\">#强制保存当前状态</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>q\t\t <span class=\"token comment\">#退出当前文档（文档必须保存才能退出）</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>q！\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">#强制退出当前文档不会修改当前内容</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>wq\t\t <span class=\"token comment\">#先保存，再退出</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>wq！\t<span class=\"token comment\">#强制保存并退出</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>x\t\t <span class=\"token comment\">#先保存，在退出</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre>ZZ\t\t <span class=\"token comment\">#保存退出，shift+zz</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"10\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>number  <span class=\"token comment\">#跳转至对应行号</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"11\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">-